$BR
\{ans_rule(25)\}
$PAR
$PAR
EOT

@answers = (interval_cmp("(0,I)"));

ANS(@answers );

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
$BR
(D) Find the \(x\)-coordinates of all local maxima of \(f\).
